
Ranger Help for: calm
=====================

SYNTAX:      calm <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   9
BASE SP:     45 sp
SKILL TYPE:  defensive

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to use his nature-like behavior to overcome
hesitation by animals and calm it. A calmed animal stops attacking, 
and anything attacking the animal stops attacking. There is a chance
that the animal will get scared and start attacking again. A Ranger
cannot calm his or her enemy race.

